From 7a57964c63f520aef9d0c46731d94fd55680e81f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ryan Hunt <rhunt@eqrion.net>
Date: Thu, 8 Aug 2024 20:49:44 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Bug 1911909 - wasm: Refactor structs and arrays to more
 closely match the spec. r=bvisness

The spec has the notion of a 'FieldType' which both struct fields
and array types share. This commit refactors them to use the same
type.

Differential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D218753
